45
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:39,010
So, you have to talk to me. Please.

46
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:43,510
No more secrets, okay?

47
00:03:46,010 --> 00:03:47,010
Okay.

48
00:03:47,100 --> 00:03:50,810
Did... did you see this thing again
on the field?

49
00:03:55,060 --> 00:03:56,060
Yes.

50
00:03:57,650 --> 00:03:59,690
What... what is it?

51
