I don't know.

52
00:04:05,530 --> 00:04:09,080
<font color="#ff00ff">[stammering]</font> It's almost
more like a feeling.

53
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:12,830
Like the one you had
that night at the arcade?

54
00:04:17,090 --> 00:04:18,340
Yes.

55
00:04:19,340 --> 00:04:21,340
<font color="#ff00ff">[stutters]</font> What does it want?

56
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:26,140
I don't know.

57
