65
00:04:47,910 --> 00:04:50,660
<font color="#ff00ff">[sobbing]</font> I just want this to be over.

66
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:54,210
It's okay. It's okay. Hey.

67
00:04:54,290 --> 00:04:56,170
- Listen. Look, look at me.
- <font color="#ff00ff">[sniffles]</font>

68
00:04:56,750 --> 00:05:01,210
I will never, ever let anything bad
happen to you ever again.

69
00:05:02,260 --> 00:05:05,970
Whatever's going on in you,
we're gonna fix it. I will fix it.

70
00:05:06,970 --> 00:05:09,300
I promise. I'm here.

71
00:05:09,390 --> 00:05:10,810
<font color="#ff00ff">[shuddering]</font>

72
00:05:36,790 --> 00:05:37,790
<font color="#ff00ff">[sighs]</font>

73
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:55,020
