00:35:31,540 --> 00:35:33,170
<font color="#ff00ff">[stations changing]</font>

477
00:35:33,250 --> 00:35:34,920
<font color="#ff00ff">[upbeat song playing]</font>

478
00:35:35,710 --> 00:35:36,750
<font color="#ff00ff">[radio static]</font>

479
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,800
<font color="#ff00ff">[Terry mumbling indistinctly]</font>

480
00:36:25,890 --> 00:36:28,390
Three to the right.
Four to the left.

481
00:36:44,530 --> 00:36:45,740
Rainbow.

482
00:36:47,030 --> 00:36:50,040
Three to the right.
Four to the left.

483
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:56,460
Rainbow.

484
00:36:56,540 --> 00:36:58,420
Three to the right.
Four to the left.

485
00:36:59,050 --> 00:37:00,250
Four-fifty...

486
00:37:07,350 --> 00:37:08,350
Jane.

487
00:37:12,810 --> 00:37:13,940
Mama?

488
00:37:27,990 --> 00:37:29,450
Mama!

489
00:37:34,210 --> 00:37:35,960
<font color="#ff00ff">[crying]</font> Mama?

